$interpreted: Aosta: Remember, I am Aosta Clovis. You are MX46.
Aosta: As could every single model before him. Nothing to be surprised about.
Aosta: ...Dietrich...can you recall anything about this person?
Aosta: Still unable to link up to his consciousness?
Aosta: Forget it. For the time being, we'll observe him.
Aosta: I have things to tend to. You, watch over him for a while.
Aosta: It's just like taking care of a baby...kind of?
Yamitsuki: What's the matter? You want something?
Yamitsuki: Wha...d-don't run around so much!
Aosta: What is going on over here?
Yamitsuki: It's a mistake on my part. Apologies...
Aosta: MX46, let me take a look.
Aosta: Good, everything seems fine. I'll strengthen your outer casing in a few days.
Aosta: If nothing else, I shall take my leave.
Yamitsuki: So it's on me again!?
Aosta: You've done it before, haven't you?
Aosta: Why are you following me?
Yamitsuki: He probably sees you...as his father?
Aosta: Quit talking nonsense. Go do what you're supposed to do.
